The '''Galderian Slave Traders''' were a group of [[Galderian/Legends|Galderians]] [[Slavery/Legends|slavers]] who hailed from [[Galdar]]. They were known to have had a base in the [[Trebodar system]] until it was destroyed by a joint [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]] and [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel Alliance]] task force. They also somehow acquired at least one [[Space ARC battle cruiser|Space ARC]], probably through enslaving the race who created them, as well as many [[I-BEAM Star Fighter]]s.

